O-Okay, there's -- there's
a cost for everything...

07:10.097 --> 07:13.559
...including having Vic
back in our lives.

07:13.684 --> 07:16.604
The Tiles are strictly
for emergencies only.

07:16.729 --> 07:17.980
For Vic.

07:18.105 --> 07:20.524
This wasn't her idea.

07:21.317 --> 07:22.485
It was mine.

07:25.071 --> 07:27.698
Hey, please, please, please.

07:28.824 --> 07:30.117
Trust me.

07:31.702 --> 07:33.746
I'm not gonna do
anything stupid.

07:33.871 --> 07:36.582
I wouldn't want
the FBI on my ass.

07:36.707 --> 07:39.210
[Sighs]

07:47.093 --> 07:48.386
[ Chuckles ]

08:13.035 --> 08:14.704
