Grandpa Chris.

08:46.027 --> 08:47.653
Hey.

08:47.778 --> 08:50.031
[ Chuckles] Hey.

08:51.282 --> 08:53.200
Boy, I am glad
to finally meet you.

08:56.078 --> 08:58.998
