09:08.424 --> 09:09.717
[ Chuckles ]

09:09.842 --> 09:13.012
Yeah, well, she's a little rough
around the edges.

09:13.137 --> 09:14.013
I'll give you that.

09:14.138 --> 09:17.183
But if you look over there,
Wayne, check it out.

09:18.309 --> 09:20.186
That's a pretty cool lake.

09:21.145 --> 09:26.150
Now, your morn liked to fish
when she was your age.

09:27.318 --> 09:29.236
What do you think?
You wanna give it a shot?

09:30.988 --> 09:33.365
Sounds like a plan.

09:33.491 --> 09:35.409
- Hmm?
- Alright.

09:35.534 --> 09:37.620
I'll show you guys around.

09:37.745 --> 09:40.289
[Birds chirping]

09:43.459 --> 09:46.462
[ Hypnotic music plays]

09:55.179 --> 09:56.972
VIC:
Come on, Bats!

10:08.484 --> 10:10.569
