are there?

10:10.694 --> 10:12.238
CHRIS: Just the lake
and the driveway.

10:13.322 --> 10:14.949
The woods, I guess,
if you're going by foot,

10:15.074 --> 10:18.619
but, well, that's a trek
from the road.

10:18.744 --> 10:21.539
VIC:
What about guns?

10:21.664 --> 10:25.000
