11:25.186 --> 11:26.937
Thank you.

11:27.062 --> 11:29.315
But, Vic, we got to do it
without the feds noticing, okay?

11:29.440 --> 11:32.067
I cannot have them
asking questions.

11:32.193 --> 11:33.986
And Wayne can't know
about this, either.

11:34.111 --> 11:37.114
We'll do it tonight
after his bedtime.

11:40.993 --> 11:42.786
We're gonna be okay.

11:42.912 --> 11:44.914
[ Chuckles ]

11:50.628 --> 11:51.879
[Sighs]

11:53.047 --> 11:54.506
Alright.

11:54.632 --> 11:56.383
