WAYNE: Dad?

44:07.312 --> 44:08.772
Where's Morn?

44:08.897 --> 44:10.649
She went to go help your
Aunt Maggie with something.

44:10.774 --> 44:13.193
She'll be right back.
Why?

44:14.403 --> 44:17.114
I think I did a bad thing.

44:17.239 --> 44:19.867
[Ominous music playing]

44:19.992 --> 44:20.993
[ Exhales heavily]

44:21.118 --> 44:22.119
VIC: Hey.

44:24.288 --> 44:25.873
You her ride?

44:27.499 --> 44:28.750
I'm glad you're okay.

44:29.877 --> 44:32.129
I had them.
I had both of them.

44:33.046 --> 44:35.465
They got away.
I'm s-- I'm sorry, Vic.

44:36.884 --> 44:38.760
[Cellphone vibrating]

44:42.014 --> 44:43.307
Hey, Carmody.

44:43.432 --> 44:44.975
We found her alive
and in one piece.

44:45.100 --> 44:47.311
<i>LOU:
Wayne's been talking to Manx.</i>

44:47.436 --> 44:48.562
What?

44:48.687 --> 44:49.980
I don't know
how the bastard did it,

44:50.105 --> 44:51.690
but he's been visiting Wayne
in his dreams,

44:51.815 --> 44:53.942
<i>talking to him, like, for real.</i>

44:54.067 --> 44:55.068
The candy cane.

44:55.194 --> 44:57.112
<i>LOU:
He knows where we are, Vic.</i>

44:57.237 --> 44:58.989
<i>Wayne to/d him.</i>

44:59.114 --> 45:00.407
I'm coming.

45:00.532 --> 45:02.409
Do not let Wayne
get into that car.

45:04.119 --> 45:06.121
[Sighs heavily]
